Detailed Description

The class for MGLBRep constructor of osculating circles.

This class is used for MGLBRep constructor: MGLBRep( ///BLGCS const MGLBRepEndC& begin, ///Begin end condition const MGLBRepEndC& end, ///End end conditoion const MGBPointSeq& points, ///Point seq data const int* point_kind, ///Point kind of above point. const MGOscuCircle& circle, ///Provides osculating circle data. int &error); ///Error flag. Defines OscuCircle data, index of BPointSeq points and circle radius.
